(Speed To Lead) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(# Speed-to-Lead Framework) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## Target) Tj
T*
(Reply to new leads in under 10 minutes \(ideal: under 5 minutes\).) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## Message formula) Tj
T*
(1. Acknowledge context quickly) Tj
T*
(2. Clarify their primary outcome) Tj
T*
(3. Offer one simple next step) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## Example) Tj
T*
(Hey [Name] — saw your message about [topic].) Tj
T*
(Are you currently trying to solve [pain A] or [pain B] first?) Tj
T*
(Once I know that, I can share the fastest path.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## Operational notes) Tj
T*
(- Use snippets to reduce typing delay) Tj
T*
(- Avoid paragraphs longer than 2–3 lines) Tj
T*
(- Track response time and reply rate weekly) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(See `scripts_library.md` for ready-to-use variants.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Objections) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(# Handling Price Objections) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## Core principle) Tj
T*
(Most objections reflect uncertainty, not rejection.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Use this structure:) Tj
T*
(- Outcome \(what changes\)) Tj
T*
(- Timeframe \(when it should change\)) Tj
T*
(- Proof \(why this is credible\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## Examples) Tj
T*
(### "Too expensive") Tj
T*
(Totally fair. If we could improve [metric] in [timeframe], would this feel like a clear) Tj
T*
(yes?) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(### "Need to think about it") Tj
T*
(Makes sense. Want a one-page implementation map so your decision is based on clear steps,) Tj
T*
(not guesswork?) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## Do / Don’t) Tj
T*
(- ✅ Ask clarifying questions) Tj
ET
